emuInput.TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Maude Jones, Christine Hunt, and Marie Harris, posed outside of Mt. Carmel Baptist Church for Fourth Annual Garden Party and Fashion Show, North Versailles
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 25, 1970, pg. 18 reads: "These Six Attractive Models paraded the latest in mod summer fashions at the Fourth Annual Garden Party and Fashion Show sponsored by the Mt. Carmel Baptist Church in Crestas Terrace, North Versailles, recently. Two of the models are members of the New Pittsburgh COurier's 1970 list of Ten Best Dressed Women.  Pictured from left in popular pants attire are: Mrs. Maude Jones, New Courier's Best Dressed; Miss Christine Hunt, Miss Marie Harris...- Harris Photo."
